                "paragraphSubtitles": ["Simple present: he, she, it"],
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In positive sentences, we use the main verb plus -s or -es."
                ]
              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 2,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In negative sentences, we use doesn't  plus the main verb without -s."
                ]
              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 3,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In yes/no questions, we use Does followed by the subject and the main verb without -s"
                ]
              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 4,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In short answers, we use does or doesn't."
                ]
              },
              {
                "paragraphOrdinal": 5,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "In wh- questions, we use a question word and does plus the main verb without -s."
                ]
              }
